# M1S2Projet: Multivariate Polynomial Interpolation & Vanishing Ideal Computation

This project computes the **vanishing ideal** of a finite set of points in â„Â² (and extends to â„Â³) using Lagrangeâ€style interpolation and linear algebra. It automatically generates all polynomials that vanish on a given point set and provides visualization tools.

